**Summary:** Documents how to configure single sign-on (SSO) in Amplitude using custom or unlisted SAML 2.0 compliant identity providers through the "Other" option in Organization Settings > Access & SSO Settings, requiring metadata file upload and manual entry of entity ID and assertion consumer service URL.

